<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 00:35:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列女足在欧洲锦标赛上遭到亲巴勒斯坦抗议者的骚扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-soccer-team-harassed-by-pro-palestine-protesters-at-european-championship/0000018f-d9d8-dbdb-a59f-d9d9cdb00000</link><description>“当以色列正在进行种族灭绝时，苏格兰接待以色列女队是可耻的”：以色列足球运动员在格拉斯哥的这场有争议的比赛中被跟踪，拒绝进入训练场，并拒绝奏国歌</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 20:21:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-womens-soccer-team-harassed-by-pro-palestine-protesters-at-european-championship/0000018f-d9d8-dbdb-a59f-d9d9cdb00000</guid></item><item><title>选举民意调查：甘茨当选总理，反对党赢得69个席位，内塔尼亚胡赢得51个席位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/elections-poll-gantz-favored-as-pm-opposition-bloc-win-69-seats-over-netanyahus-51/0000018f-da36-d673-ab8f-fffe578a0000</link><description>38% 的受访者表示，他们认为甘茨会成为更好的总理，低于 1 月份的 46%；而 30% 的受访者支持内塔尼亚胡，高于上次民意调查的 24%</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 19:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/elections-poll-gantz-favored-as-pm-opposition-bloc-win-69-seats-over-netanyahus-51/0000018f-da36-d673-ab8f-fffe578a0000</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫因加沙战争禁止以色列人入境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/maldives-to-ban-israelis-from-entering-the-country-over-the-war-in-gaza/0000018f-da12-d573-af8f-da7f1b890000</link><description>马尔代夫是一个与以色列没有正式外交关系的逊尼派穆斯林国家，由于公众对加沙战争的愤怒上升，马尔代夫决定禁止以色列护照持有者入境。该国是以色列人喜爱的旅游目的地，去年有近 11,000 人到访</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 18:04:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/maldives-to-ban-israelis-from-entering-the-country-over-the-war-in-gaza/0000018f-da12-d573-af8f-da7f1b890000</guid></item><item><title>邀请内塔尼亚胡到华盛顿，民主党领导人在背后捅了以色列自由派一刀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-02/ty-article/.highlight/inviting-netanyahu-to-d-c-democratic-leaders-stabbed-israels-liberals-in-the-back/0000018f-d9ac-d5bc-a1bf-dfbca6210000</link><description>帮助内塔尼亚胡在国会发表讲话并不是“亲以色列”，因为他知道自10月7日以来，他一直没有时间会见在他的监督下被哈马斯入侵的任何以色列社区</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 17:37:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-02/ty-article/.highlight/inviting-netanyahu-to-d-c-democratic-leaders-stabbed-israels-liberals-in-the-back/0000018f-d9ac-d5bc-a1bf-dfbca6210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争第 240 天：埃及称以色列必须撤出拉法过境点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-240-israel-must-pull-out-of-rafah-crossing-egypt-says/0000018f-d9d5-d5bc-a1bf-dff5d2560001</link><description>内塔尼亚胡高级顾问称拜登周五提出停火建议的演讲具有“政治性” ■ 接近总理的消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡总理试图绕过国家调查委员会 10 月 7 日的正常程序 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列正在准备一个替代管理机构加沙挑战哈马斯 ■ 战争进入 240 天后您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-240-israel-must-pull-out-of-rafah-crossing-egypt-says/0000018f-d9d5-d5bc-a1bf-dff5d2560001</guid></item><item><title>需要几代人的时间才能恢复：演员迈克尔·道格拉斯 (Michael Douglas) 访问 10 月 7 日遭受严重损失的以色列基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/actor-michael-douglas-visits-israeli-kibbutz-that-suffered-heavy-loses-on-oct-7/0000018f-d989-dbdb-a59f-d9c92c4b0000</link><description>这位奥斯卡获奖明星开始了他的以色列之旅，首先参观了加沙边境的贝埃里基布兹，10 月 7 日，这里有近 100 人被杀，另有 26 人被扣为人质，然后前往特拉维夫参加摄影展</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/actor-michael-douglas-visits-israeli-kibbutz-that-suffered-heavy-loses-on-oct-7/0000018f-d989-dbdb-a59f-d9c92c4b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列前外交部长兼副总理戴维·利维去世，享年 86 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/david-levy-former-israeli-foreign-minister-and-deputy-pm-dies-at-86/00000189-9cf1-d00f-a7db-bdfbe8af0000</link><description>作为利库德集团前领导人，利维在议会任职四十年，并担任外交部长、住房部长以及回归和一体化部长。作为 2018 年以色列奖获得者，利维“是最早表达许多人对分配和社会正义要求的人之一”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 16:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/david-levy-former-israeli-foreign-minister-and-deputy-pm-dies-at-86/00000189-9cf1-d00f-a7db-bdfbe8af0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们永远拥有墨西哥”：以色列国家足球队在 1970 年世界杯上表现出色的不为人知的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-untold-story-of-israels-marvelous-national-soccer-team-in-the-1970-world-cup/0000018f-d8a2-d513-a9af-fef2301a0000</link><description>一部以色列电视连续剧以新的视角展示了足球领域的独特成就，同时也展示了“以色列充满自豪感、感觉无所不能、在世界上超级受欢迎”的时代</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 15:45:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-06-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-untold-story-of-israels-marvelous-national-soccer-team-in-the-1970-world-cup/0000018f-d8a2-d513-a9af-fef2301a0000</guid></item><item><title>“不投降，不向美国压力，不向任何事情投降”：内塔尼亚胡部长在纽约断然拒绝拜登停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-calling-for-immediate-hostage-deal-will-lead-new-yorks-israel-day-parade/0000018f-d8da-d513-a9af-fefabceb0000</link><description>在纽约的以色列日游行中，超过 3,000 名游行者与人质家属一起呼吁立即达成协议，释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质。美国多数党领袖查克·舒默在游行前表示，“在把他们带回家之前，我们决不能退缩”</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 13:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/thousands-calling-for-immediate-hostage-deal-will-lead-new-yorks-israel-day-parade/0000018f-d8da-d513-a9af-fefabceb0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登令人震惊的停火和人质协议提案旨在结束以色列与哈马斯在加沙的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/inside-bidens-shock-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal-proposal-to-end-israel-hamas-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d8ca-d513-a9af-fefa73210000</link><description>无论美国总统乔·拜登周五宣布的停火提案来自华盛顿还是耶路撒冷，现在很明显，全世界都将结束加沙战争的尝试视为“拜登的协议”，而他则将自己置于危险之中，就像从未</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 13:29:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/inside-bidens-shock-cease-fire-and-hostage-deal-proposal-to-end-israel-hamas-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d8ca-d513-a9af-fefa73210000</guid></item><item><title>表演行动主义的真正影响？ 《All Eyes on Rafah》如何在 Instagram 上引起轰动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/how-all-eyes-on-rafah-became-an-instagram-sensation/0000018f-d854-dbdb-a59f-d95d9d220000</link><description>这张由人工智能生成的图像在一周内被分享了近 5000 万次，在中东引起了赞扬和批评，也遭到了以色列影响者的反攻</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/how-all-eyes-on-rafah-became-an-instagram-sensation/0000018f-d854-dbdb-a59f-d95d9d220000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院出庭，总统赫尔佐格出庭：内塔尼亚胡计划于 10 月 7 日进行国家调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/top-court-out-president-herzog-in-netanyahus-plan-for-state-inquiry-into-october-7/0000018f-d89d-dd44-a3ef-db9d15ee0000</link><description>接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士告诉国土报，他担心代理最高法院院长将任命前法院院长埃丝特·哈尤特领导国家调查委员会</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/top-court-out-president-herzog-in-netanyahus-plan-for-state-inquiry-into-october-7/0000018f-d89d-dd44-a3ef-db9d15ee0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管存在缺陷，拜登的提议为加沙“永恒战争”提供了替代方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/despite-faults-bidens-proposal-offers-an-alternative-to-eternal-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d83c-db0d-a98f-dc7d79b50000</link><description>该提案提出的时机和方式清楚地表明了白宫希望结束战争的愿望。如果加沙的哈马斯领导层同意，该组织的其他领导人也会这样做</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:13:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/despite-faults-bidens-proposal-offers-an-alternative-to-eternal-war-in-gaza/0000018f-d83c-db0d-a98f-dc7d79b50000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷发生大火，以色列博物馆被迫疏散</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/large-fire-breaks-out-in-jerusalem-forcing-evacuation-of-israel-museum/0000018f-d8c1-d513-a9af-fef1d38e0000</link><description>目前已派出23支消防队和8架消防飞机赶赴现场。博物馆管理层报告称，没有造成人员伤亡或财产损失，也没有艺术品受到损害</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 11:50:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/large-fire-breaks-out-in-jerusalem-forcing-evacuation-of-israel-museum/0000018f-d8c1-d513-a9af-fef1d38e0000</guid></item><item><title>与以色列一样，哈马斯并没有为巴勒斯坦人提供“后天”——只是更多的战争和苦难</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/like-israel-hamas-isnt-offering-palestinians-a-day-after-just-more-war-and-suffering/0000018f-ceb4-d323-a98f-dffdff030000</link><description>武装斗争未能阻止对巴勒斯坦土地的持续盗窃。以色列在加沙地带造成的破坏和死亡需要一种不同的斗争 — — 一种考虑到其人民的生存权的斗争</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 09:37:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/like-israel-hamas-isnt-offering-palestinians-a-day-after-just-more-war-and-suffering/0000018f-ceb4-d323-a98f-dffdff030000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院审议反对极端正统派草案豁免的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-petitions-against-draft-exemption-for-ultra-orthodox/0000018f-d789-d5f5-ad8f-f7eb94a30000</link><description>由九名法官组成的扩大小组听取了有关可能对内塔尼亚胡政府产生深远影响的问题的请愿书</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 06:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-to-hear-petitions-against-draft-exemption-for-ultra-orthodox/0000018f-d789-d5f5-ad8f-f7eb94a30000</guid></item><item><title>在制定以色列与哈马斯协议时，拜登对加沙的“后天”提出了关键问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/without-a-realistic-day-after-plan-bidens-proposal-is-unlikely-to-succeed/0000018f-d59a-d034-ab8f-f79f1cf20000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡必须在协议的第一阶段决定由谁来管理加沙地带。如果他继续回避巴勒斯坦权力机构，哈马斯将填补这一真空</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 02:59:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article/.premium/without-a-realistic-day-after-plan-bidens-proposal-is-unlikely-to-succeed/0000018f-d59a-d034-ab8f-f79f1cf20000</guid></item><item><title>叙利亚北部发生爆炸，多人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article-live/ben-gvir-smotrich-threaten-to-quit-netanyahu-coalition-if-biden-proposal-accepted/0000018f-d5ea-d673-ab8f-f7eae1b10000</link><description>马尔代夫将因加沙战争而禁止以色列人进入该国 ■ 反坦克导弹击中以色列北部地区 ■ 国防部长加兰特：以色列正在加沙准备替代统治机构，挑战哈马斯 ■ 火箭弹袭击后，以色列北部爆发火灾来自黎巴嫩 ■ 黎巴嫩官方媒体报道称，以色列在边境附近发动袭击，造成两人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 02:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-02/ty-article-live/ben-gvir-smotrich-threaten-to-quit-netanyahu-coalition-if-biden-proposal-accepted/0000018f-d5ea-d673-ab8f-f7eae1b10000</guid></item><item><title>“拜登的提议是彻底失败”：本-格维尔、斯莫特里奇拒绝美国人质提议，威胁退出内塔尼亚胡联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-smotrich-reject-u-s-hostage-proposal-threaten-to-quit-netanyahu-coalition/0000018f-d552-d5bc-a1bf-df7225960000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡拒绝加沙永久停火，而甘茨则要求战时内阁召开会议讨论美国的提议。反对党领袖拉皮德向总理提供“安全网”，以便在他的极右翼盟友退出政府的情况下确保人质协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 20:57:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-smotrich-reject-u-s-hostage-proposal-threaten-to-quit-netanyahu-coalition/0000018f-d552-d5bc-a1bf-df7225960000</guid></item><item><title>多特蒙德与向以色列出售武器的军火制造商的赞助协议引发抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/dortmunds-sponsorship-deal-with-arms-maker-selling-weapons-to-israel-sparks-protest/0000018f-d533-d673-ab8f-f7fb15840000</link><description>周六对阵皇家马德里的欧洲冠军联赛决赛前几个小时，针对多特蒙德足球俱乐部与莱茵金属公司的交易举行了抗议，莱茵金属公司被认为是欧洲最大的武器出口商</description><pubDate>Sat, 01 Jun 2024 19:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-01/ty-article/.premium/dortmunds-sponsorship-deal-with-arms-maker-selling-weapons-to-israel-sparks-protest/0000018f-d533-d673-ab8f-f7fb15840000</guid></item></channel></rss>